delete_cell_stack_group(25.10)                  delete_cell_stack_group(25.10)

Name
       delete_cell_stack_group - Deletes cell stack group definition

Syntax
       delete_cell_stack_group

       [-help]

       [-name <group_name>]

       Deletes cell stack group definition.

Parameters
       -name <group_name>
              Specifies the group(s) for which the cell stack group definition
              is to be deleted.

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each delete_cell_stack_group parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man delete_cell_stack_group

